SUMMARY:ENRG HTX - June 2026
DESCRIPTION:Register here: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/enrg-htx-june-2026-tickets-1990513456331 \nENRG (Entrepreneurial Networking Resource Group) is a community for entrepreneurs with 10-250 employees running on EOS or EOS Curious. \n\n\n\n\nENRG (pronounced energy) is here to stay in Houston! \nErick Garcia\, Lesa A Skipper and Craig Ceccanti are teaming up to build the Houston ENRG Chapter and we could not be more excited to invite entrepreneurs running on EOS or EOS Curious to this collaborative room! Join us on June 19th at 8:30am at the Ion District (Downstairs 028) for the first meeting! \nWhat is ENRG?\nThe vision is to establish an ENRG (Entrepreneurial Networking Resource Group) in Houston for entrepreneurs with 10-250 employees. This is a free EOS Worldwide aligned community for entrepreneurs led by one EOS Implementer and one Integrator. \nEach monthly meeting includes:\n– Practical training on an EOS tools\n– Peer-to-peer issue solving\n– Valuable networking\n– Content that helps move the needle on your business\n– Exposure to Subject Matter Experts\nNo sales pitches here though\, we’re here to help all tides rise! \nThis is WHERE entrepreneurs find the WHOs and the HOWs to move their business forward.
URL:https://iondistrict.com/event/enrg-htx-june-2026/
LOCATION:Ion – Conference Room 028\, 4201 Main St.\, Houston\, TX\, 77002\, United States
CATEGORIES:3rd Party Registration
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://iondistrict.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/ENRG-June.webp
END:VEVENT
